[For a map of the Czech Republic see https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=5207022,110

Follow-up report No 5 was submitted by the Czech Republic to the OIE on Tue 25 Jul 2017. It included the data of 12 new cases, all discovered in the Zlínský province that added to the previous 50 cases, bring the total to 62 ASF-confirmed wild boar.
http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review?page_refer=MapFullEventReport&reportid=24405.

The disease continues its spread also in Russia; see http://tass.com/economy/957645. - Mod.AS

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=5207022,112.]
